@jvhurley @DroughtGov @NOAA @NOAAClimate @NOAANCEIclimate @USDAClimateHubs @USDA @NWSCPC @NWS @stateclimate @WRCCclimate @NWSWestern Great Q, John: The most exceptional drought (D4) coverage recorded in California in the USDM's 21-year is 58.41% (14 times in 2014). 

